name: Arcadia villa
address: Bakbakan, Gianyar, Gianyar Regency, Bali 80515, Indonesia
review 1: Exceptional villa that exceeded all our expectations. Quiet, great views, spacious and good service.
review 2:
Arcadia Villa it’s very very nice place; at middle of rice field; be said river,
Villa Cascara is close to Ubud, temples, yoga centres, seaside, parks, restaurants etc. You’ll love it because the location is very interesting if you want to experience the authentic local rhythm, with views towards the rice fields and the jungle! The outdoors is friendly with several spots to relax and be inventive! Indoors is spacious with amazing design elements. Is good for couples, big groups, families, adventurers and business travelers. The staff that stays there can take care of you.
review 3:
Friendly and helpful staff.
The rooms were spacious and comfortable.
Huge swimming pools all for yourself.
Bamboo house is really nice, you would not find this kind of property in other villa, You can ask the staff to book spa in villa, it is a whole new experience !
Located in middle of rice field, the view is really EXCEPTIONAL !
review 4: My family stayed at the villa for 7 weeks at the end of a round the world trip. It is a lovely place to stay: beautiful villa, lovely gardens and pool and the bamboo hut for yoga etc. The team are very helpful and can help with car and scooter rental, yoga teachers and massage as wanted. The villa is peaceful, located at the back of the village in the paddy fields offering great views.
review 5:
Place for teach your children about nature. Rice field view, jungle and river view. Many flower plants, coconut, soursop, papaya (you can make papaya salad ^^) and many more.
Don't forget to enjoy the sunset with a cup of tea or coffee in the large terrace or bamboo house.
If you lucky to come in the rice planting season, you can follow to local people, how to plant the rice.
Rice field growth season, it's a green season makes your eyes very comfortable and peaceful.
Harvest season, is excited season, you will see the farmer very excited in this season.
Plowing season, it's wonderful too, you will see many storks follow the farmer to get some worm from the soil.
Humble and helpful staff will make your perfect holiday is unforgettable.
